Na ivo wandugu zangu, kwaviya chonda chiweng'higwe na malagilizo yayo, acheni chihovugwe uhasanyi wa lukuli na wa muhe. Cheye chizakuwa welile kwa kumdumba Mulungu.
Mwing'heni hanhu muna mizoyo yenu. Hatuchimtendele munhu yoyose vihile, hatuchimtendele chihile munhu yoyose, na hatuchimtendile chinhu chihile munhu yoyose.
Ndangulonga ivo kwaviya nowatagusa mweye kuwa na wihe. Kwaviya nolonga mwanduso, mweye mwii mizoyo yetu, muladi mukale hamwe hebu mukale hamwe.
