Ivo mweye wagane, kwaviya mvimanyile sambi vinhu vino, muilole! Sekemusolelekelekwe na uhasanyi wa wanhu waja wohambe wamtegeleze, na sekemugwile kulawa mwiikaye yenu midala.
Mbali mukale muna ubazi na mbuli za Mndewa na Mlohozi wetu Yesu Chilisito. Yatogoligwe yeye sambi na siku zose. Amin.
Na chiya chayalongile kulawa kwandusila, chiya chiya chihulike na chiya chiya chiwona kwa meso yetu, chiya chiya chiya chiya chiwonile na makono yetu chayadalisa kwa mbuli ya mbuli ya ugima.
